author: Tyler Estep
title: Shooting reported during traffic stop on I-75 in Bartow County
text:
Authorities are investigating a possible shooting during a traffic stop on I-75 north in Bartow County.
A Georgia State Patrol spokesman said the Emerson Police Department was “on a traffic stop with shots fired” near Ga. 113. The Bartow County Sheriff’s Office and Cartersville Police Department were also on scene.
—Please return to AJC.com for updates.
